SET description = 'This whitepaper presents an independent, critical analysis of AI adoption in executive contexts, challenging conventional transformation narratives with evidence from 500+ C-suite interactions across global markets. Author examines the significant gap between public AI success stories and private implementation realities, revealing that while 65% of organizations report regular AI use, most executives expect only 30% of experiments to scale successfully.
The analysis exposes critical challenges including attribution difficulties, cultural resistance patterns, and methodological limitations in current AI research. Drawing from major surveys by McKinsey, Deloitte, and PwC, plus extensive field experience, the paper provides practical frameworks for cultural intelligence assessment and AI readiness evaluation.
Rather than promotional enthusiasm, this research emphasizes intellectual honesty about implementation challenges, offering executives evidence-based guidance for navigating AI adoption uncertainties. The work includes detailed case studies of discontinued initiatives, regional variation analysis, and actionable recommendations for systematic AI experimentation approaches.'
WHERE title = 'The Algorithmic C-Suite: How AI is Reshaping Executive Decision Architecture in 2025';